COLORATION (
Fig. 95
). Dorsal and lateral sides of prozonites greyish, dorsolateral and ventrolateral sides with yellowish spots. Metazonites anteriorly greyish, posteriorly brownish, laterally with yellowish spots, ventrolaterally yellowish. First few body segments darker.

